.Dd May 3, 2026
.Dt CRATE-HUB 8
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm crate-hub
.Nd central aggregator for multi-host crate(8) deployments
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Nm
.Op Fl f
.Op Fl c Ar config
.Op Fl p Ar port
.Op Fl w Ar webdir
.Sh DESCRIPTION
.Nm
polls
.Xr crated 8
instances on a list of remote nodes, caches their state in a
SQLite store, and serves an aggregated REST API plus an embedded
web dashboard. It is the single pane of glass for an operator
running containers on multiple hosts.
.Pp
The hub itself does not proxy mutating requests
.Po
.Ic POST
to start/stop/restart a container, etc.
.Pc :
the dashboard hits each node's
.Xr crated 8
directly so the
.Em admin
Bearer token never leaves the operator's browser. The hub is
read-mostly aggregator.
.Pp
The options are as follows:
.Bl -tag -width Ds
.It Fl f , Fl Fl foreground
Stay in the foreground; do not fork.
.It Fl c Ar config , Fl Fl config Ar config
Path to the YAML configuration file. Default
.Pa /usr/local/etc/crate-hub.conf .
.It Fl p Ar port
TCP port to listen on. Default
.Ar 9810 .
.It Fl w Ar webdir
Directory served as the embedded dashboard. Default
.Pa /usr/local/share/crate-hub/web .
.El
.Sh ENDPOINTS
.Bl -tag -width "POST /api/v1/admin/prune                  "
.It GET Pa /healthz
Liveness check.
.It GET Pa /api/v1/nodes
List configured nodes with their last-poll reachability and
last-error string.
.It GET Pa /api/v1/nodes/:host/containers
Container list reported by a specific node.
.It GET Pa /api/v1/containers
All containers across all nodes, grouped by node.
.It GET Pa /api/v1/aggregate
Single-shot summary for the dashboard banner: nodes total /
reachable / down, containers total.
.It GET Pa /metrics
Prometheus exposition aggregating all nodes.
.It POST Pa /api/v1/admin/prune
Drop store entries older than 48 hours.
.El
.Sh CONFIGURATION
.Bd -literal -offset indent
listen_port: 9810

# Polling interval for each node, seconds.
poll_interval: 15

nodes:
  - name:  alpha
    host:  alpha.example.com
    port:  9800
    token: <admin-token-for-alpha>
  - name:  beta
    host:  beta.example.com
    port:  9800
    token: <admin-token-for-beta>
.Ed
.Sh WEB DASHBOARD
The
.Pa /usr/local/share/crate-hub/web
directory ships
.Pa index.html ,
.Pa app.js ,
and
.Pa style.css .
The page polls
.Pa /api/v1/aggregate ,
.Pa /api/v1/nodes ,
and
.Pa /api/v1/containers
every five seconds. Mutating actions
.Pq Ic start , Ic stop , Ic restart , Ic destroy
hit the per-node
.Xr crated 8
directly via
.Ic fetch ;
the operator pastes an admin Bearer token on first use and the
browser keeps it in
.Ar localStorage .
.Sh FILES
.Bl -tag -width "/usr/local/share/crate-hub/web/index.html"
.It Pa /usr/local/etc/crate-hub.conf
Operator-edited config file.
.It Pa /var/db/crate-hub/metrics.db
SQLite store of polled metrics.
.It Pa /usr/local/share/crate-hub/web/index.html
Embedded dashboard root.
.El
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr crate 5 ,
.Xr crated 8 ,
.Xr jls 8
.Sh HISTORY
The
.Nm
service first appeared in crate version 0.4.0; the embedded web
dashboard landed in 0.6.7.
